General.Name: Tempest Security AB
General.Description: Tempest Security AB (publ) provides security services worldwide. The company operates through two segments, Security Solutions and Risk Solutions. It offers risk solutions, which include consulting, training, personnel protection, and other services; alarm and CCTV surveillance; ground transportation services; and provides SOCs as a managed service. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
